'From Squeak3.7alpha of 22 October 2003 [latest update: #5526] on 9 November 2003 at 8:13:29 am'!"Change Set:		SketchMorphEditorOpen-nkDate:			9 November 2003Author:			Ned KonzThis adds a construction method to SketchMorph that opens an editor on a blank SketchMorph."!!SketchMorph class methodsFor: 'instance creation' stamp: 'nk 11/9/2003 08:11'!openEditor	"Create a new SketchMorph and open a SketchMorphEditor on it. 	Answers the painted SketchMorph."	"SketchMorph openEditor"	| newSketch |	newSketch := (self				withForm: (Form extent: 100 @ 100 depth: Display depth)) center: self currentWorld center;				 openInWorld;				 editDrawing.	^ newSketch! !